{"tid":146074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好想箍牙但怕怕呀！ 求箍過嘅巴打絲打或者牙醫入嚟","createTime":"2017-03-06T17:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T12:03:02.000Z","uid":35906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce5e58590f1f23b6d477fc78bb395dc39128bf5","tid":146074,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:43:16.000Z","msg":"我一直都好想箍牙<br />\n但我本身智慧齒生得唔靚 不過就無唔舒服嗰啲<br />\n但如果去箍牙 應該一定要開刀剝牙<br />\n我好怕要開刀呀 好恐怖 我上面棚牙可能可以唔洗剝，但下面棚牙就要 <br />\n加上剝牙之後塊面會尖啲瘦啲 好嚮往呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以要求剝其他牙？"},{"pid":"1a7c6a5a9ff63dfce641d37ed2998677ddac7200","tid":146074,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"真心求指教呀 拍爛檔吖"},{"pid":"9fda2e1c0ae3a2182fb27fa7ef902bfe63c70829","tid":146074,"uid":52543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"想箍牙留名<br />\n<br />\n大家邊到箍<br />\n同埋大概幾錢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c289bbfc14b795659944fe26b75406fd26eeec1c","tid":146074,"uid":19982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:02:58.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9c51b40cdd226ac8def4f517f12d5cf66f504968","tid":146074,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"418e4aa8b7b0c377d75bb5b06468d1114b68c787","tid":146074,"uid":1815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:06:18.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e9b8e9fc7f90806efcc0fd880ce53a7e8b70b81e","tid":146074,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:13:36.000Z","msg":"貴"},{"pid":"79e418716e96565d04d7755bbdf56d25770c54e3","tid":146074,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:17:18.000Z","msg":"剝牙要開刀？<br />\n你係咪當左正顎手術？"},{"pid":"f71de50a13aa0fbc8879b23ce035e635533dcdf3","tid":146074,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剝牙要開刀？<br />\n你係咪當左正顎手術？</blockquote><br />\n智慧齒如果生得唔靚或者出唔到嚟 牙醫會開刀𠝹開牙肉㗎"},{"pid":"e98177ac597c54bfb8954c8711ae45831221f6ca","tid":146074,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開刀冇野怕,我果陣成隻智慧齒打橫生<br />\n<br />\n後尾打麻醉針,開刀整碎佢再分件拎出黎最後縫針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但過程完全冇感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勁怕feel到佢𠝹我牙肉同縫針 成件事好恐怖"},{"pid":"fe2a59fedb17aee5412c080e13478cd126752788","tid":146074,"uid":86476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:23:29.000Z","msg":"我計埋智慧齒既話剝左六隻牙<br />\n其實剝牙唔算真係好痛架咋，最痛都係打麻醉個下，之後真係無咩feel<br />\n係上箍之後頭一兩個星期d牙會好酸痛，係痛撚到你唔會想食任何固體食物既痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過過左之後就ok 之後都唔會特別唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n利申 箍左一年"},{"pid":"bbdd2da53455b97c0de275adc5755b5bfdce24c5","tid":146074,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:24:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8e4299f733d01930c760c93fde44db078c680a8","tid":146074,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:24:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6515e36b89602b4c15da86c81ff7d5bb636a05bd","tid":146074,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:25:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0c1b2d4315b83f3fe87e8c1a01a838261edb763","tid":146074,"uid":86476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一直都好想箍牙<br />\n但我本身智慧齒生得唔靚 不過就無唔舒服嗰啲<br />\n但如果去箍牙 應該一定要開刀剝牙<br />\n我好怕要開刀呀 好恐怖 我上面棚牙可能可以唔洗剝，但下面棚牙就要 <br />\n加上剝牙之後塊面會尖啲瘦啲 好嚮往呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以要求剝其他牙？</blockquote><br />\n我有d fd話面形有變到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過塊包包面依然仲好包 一開始會因為牙仔好酸痛唔想食野所以瘦左 但之後適應左就會肥返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2201eb138e2da8da9cdf049e29b209e2bed30f5d","tid":146074,"uid":86476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我計埋智慧齒既話剝左六隻牙<br />\n其實剝牙唔算真係好痛架咋，最痛都係打麻醉個下，之後真係無咩feel<br />\n係上箍之後頭一兩個星期d牙會好酸痛，係痛撚到你唔會想食任何固體食物既痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過過左之後就ok 之後都唔會特別唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n利申 箍左一年</blockquote><br />\n你做傳統果隻家透明牙套果隻</blockquote><br />\n我做傳統呀"},{"pid":"7020a135a233ab2b0eb3ba68425bdf63b46c6010","tid":146074,"uid":7004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:29:24.000Z","msg":"過來人話你知<br />\n開刀輕鬆過你剝其他牙<br />\n因為開刀落麻醉藥一定重手啲 無feel<br />\n但剝牙麻醉落得輕手 佢起勢咁擰 個刻真係想死左佢算"},{"pid":"0c530894bb968682274921ee0672ba520c5c7160","tid":146074,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:31:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"782b21d2564629b71d1fab69c7a10e4698a9974c","tid":146074,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:38:29.000Z","msg":"係咪可以要求佢磨牙㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e070f9151ba234c2b28472c4761bbd386af71a","tid":146074,"uid":85164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:43:25.000Z","msg":"我上星期見完醫生， 要mok 四隻。最基本果四隻，<br />\n上下各兩隻，箍二年。<br />\n邊明線果款。22000$ 第一次比500$以包哂mok 牙同麻醉，<br />\n 之後每個月最少比100$, 總之拆果日比哂尾數。<br />\n有n 個朋友呢間箍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7aae746d491fcc84ee1e3583eb98238a93afb1e","tid":146074,"uid":86476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我計埋智慧齒既話剝左六隻牙<br />\n其實剝牙唔算真係好痛架咋，最痛都係打麻醉個下，之後真係無咩feel<br />\n係上箍之後頭一兩個星期d牙會好酸痛，係痛撚到你唔會想食任何固體食物既痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過過左之後就ok 之後都唔會特別唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n利申 箍左一年</blockquote><br />\n你做傳統果隻家透明牙套果隻</blockquote><br />\n我做傳統呀</blockquote><br />\n我都就黎上箍<br />\n<br />\n本身應該12月尾箍,但我1月中要旅行,拖到2月頭<br />\n<br />\n依家3月中同4月尾又去旅行都唔知仲箍唔箍好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個牙醫應該想屌我好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌我又係成日俾牙醫屌<br />\n因為我要一個月覆一次診 但係成日懶唔去 <br />\n有次拖左幾個月先去 俾牙醫屌到成間診所都知<br />\n<br />\n你箍一年定兩年啊？<br />\n快d上箍快d箍完啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58232827197937ff373f76f56b589a74f0ebfad","tid":146074,"uid":85164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上星期見完醫生， 要mok 四隻。最基本果四隻，<br />\n上下各兩隻，箍二年。<br />\n邊明線果款。22000$ 第一次比500$以包哂mok 牙同麻醉，<br />\n 之後每個月最少比100$, 總之拆果日比哂尾數。<br />\n有n 個朋友呢間箍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上星期見完醫生， 要mok 四隻。最基本果四隻，<br />\n上下各兩隻，箍二年。<br />\n邊明<span style=\"color: red;\">粒</span>果款。22000$ 第一次比500$以包哂mok 牙同麻醉，<br />\n 之後每個月最少比100$, 總之拆果日比哂尾數。<br />\n有n 個朋友呢間箍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2fd93d5ae7a63250c0ce4629ef6bc5d1f1d800","tid":146074,"uid":85164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我上星期見完醫生， 要mok 四隻。最基本果四隻，<br />\n上下各兩隻，箍二年。<br />\n邊明線果款。22000$ 第一次比500$以包哂mok 牙同麻醉，<br />\n 之後每個月最少比100$, 總之拆果日比哂尾數。<br />\n有n 個朋友呢間箍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上星期見完醫生， 要mok 四隻。最基本果四隻，<br />\n上下各兩隻，箍二年。<br />\n邊明<span style=\"color: red;\">粒</span>果款。22000$ 第一次比500$以包哂mok 牙同麻醉，<br />\n 之後每個月最少比100$, 總之拆果日比哂尾數。<br />\n有n 個朋友